{"tid":1468693,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"想講吓心理健康","createTime":"2019-08-13T20:00:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T20:15:53.000Z","uid":305779,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0f53c379bfd39463b2dacf052fc43ddb75b3993c","tid":1468693,"uid":305779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:00:30.000Z","msg":"各位<br />\n雖然香港依加越嚟越嚴峻<br />\n我地唔單止要對抗政府<br />\n仲有警狗，共黨，網軍<br />\n大家都明白各位手足都身心俱疲<br />\n付出好多時間同心血<br />\n但係政府都唔理9我地<br />\n呢場運動已經出現犧牲者啦<br />\n我實在唔想再見到再有無辜嘅犧牲<br />\n大家為香港捍衛未來嘅同時<br />\n為身邊嘅手足打氣<br />\n一定唔可以諗唔開輕生！！！！<br />\n<br />\n有咩唔開心<br />\n一定要講出嚟或者用其他方法抒壓<br />\n收埋係心裏面會爆煲<br />\n見到附近有手足情緒失控<br />\n一定要幫手<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"></span>因為香港人一個都不能少！<br />\n無論之後嘅每一場運動<br />\n大家都要撐住<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港人獅子山精神<br />\n永不言敗"},{"pid":"ec2eb23c387d58aa341742384456435ffa70d63a","tid":1468693,"uid":305779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:02:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"00d8263b93583aaeae124b6e5ad0216bd717618e","tid":1468693,"uid":305779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:03:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f32c8418224eaa8ab7570de911607edb520e068c","tid":1468693,"uid":305779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:03:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5940901c9348f9126aaad02fd19ba0b425407a16","tid":1468693,"uid":305779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:03:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a5b9afce6c04dde2472e474543670931a25b01de","tid":1468693,"uid":305779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:03:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fc981f5de9e7f8a624c252656570e0192a95319a","tid":1468693,"uid":305779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:03:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e1666697658e1a4341a57a11ae28e3ce9d2dcdff","tid":1468693,"uid":305779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:04:01.000Z","ms